WEBVTT

00:00.162 --> 00:02.395
She's found us.

00:02.862 --> 00:06.195
And I thought it was just to hurt Aidan,
but it's more than that.

00:06.299 --> 00:08.733
She wants to be him.

00:08.835 --> 00:12.464
And she wants
to live for real this time.

00:19.946 --> 00:24.110
You tell me,
who can help me?

00:24.217 --> 00:25.514
Who?

00:25.618 --> 00:27.609
I'm sure there's a rational...

00:27.720 --> 00:30.348
You take his picture
and tell me why she's in it.

00:30.456 --> 00:32.788
- Rachel.
- You take his picture.

00:32.892 --> 00:35.759
It's proof that he's what?
He's got a ghost inside him?

00:36.663 --> 00:40.565
No. The proof is what will happen.

